{"word":"οἴκτιστος","slug":"οἴκτιστος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>οἴκτιστος</b></el> <el>(οἴκτιστος, η, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:irregular'>irreg.</a> <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> of <a href='S:οἰκτρός'><el>οἰκτρός</el></a> (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>αἰσχρός,  αἴσχιστος</el>) \n<p/><i>most pitiable, lamentable</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>:—<a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>οἴκτιστα</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/>"}]}